    ${sb_menu}=    Enter Secure Boot Menu And Return Construction
    Disable Secure Boot    ${sb_menu}
    # Save Changes And Reset
    # Changes to Secure Boot menu takes action immediately, so we can just reset
    Reset System

    # 4. Check SB state in OS
